---
By: Paul of Tarsus
Locus:
  Page: 44
  Verse: 4
Tags:
  - ''
---
God is not to be fooled; a man reaps what he sows. If he sows seed in the
field of his lower nature, he will reap from it a harvest of corruption,
but if he sows in the field of spirit, the spirit will bring him a harvest
of eternal life.
